                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-94-victim835 t18310908-94-viclabel526"></join>. On the 27th of August, about eleven o'clock in the day, my cart stood in <placeName id="t18310908-94-crimeloc527">St. Paul's-church-yard</placeName>
