                     <interp inst="t18310908-94-person838" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I took the prisoner with the coat under his arm - he said it was his, and he was going to take it home.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I asked a young man to show me the way to St. James'-Park; as I went on with him he stopped and gave me the coat to hold, while he went up an alley.</p>

